{"type": "article", "id": 16815, "title": "文具套件", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-30T07:20:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143736csUIV9Nirba0dkSm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是装桌上文具的套件，有笔筒、文具盒、透明胶带的底座、名片盒、插手机的架子……几乎能够收纳桌面上所见的所有小文具。罗马尼亚设计师 Dragos Motica 用了他擅长的软木塞，搭配白色的铝做盖子，有一种手工感。在盒子侧面可以看到一些圆孔，让这组套件多了一份可爱。单个物件售价在 12 欧元到 24 欧元之间，<a href=\"http://ubikubi.ro/product/niu-desk-organizer/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144112leBSIcquZgWDEmsV.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"402\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144112wycEuWCNzORn4jdZ.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261441139gY8JPISHtGEb3Zc.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144113D0Gbia1FvPrXBw5m.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"437\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}